DLV3NoArg --> Winner : Compared
UNet --> Winner : Compared
SegFormer --> Winner : WINNER
ForkSeg --> Winner : Compared

note bottom of Winner
  SegFormer Selected
  ==
  Reasons:
  - Highest IoU: 0.85
  - Best Dice: 0.91
  - Accuracy: 95%
  - Fast inference
  - Production ready
  ==
  File: segformer_wound.pth
  Size: ~100MB
end note

@enduml
